title: Endosymbiosis and the structure of ecosystems 3

content.description: Relationships between organisms of different species shape the structure of communities and ecosystems.
content.question:
Interdependence of organisms exists at all levels of ecosystems.

Identify the trophic levels of each of the organisms in the following food web.

Predict the effect on the ecosystem if the rabbits were removed and explain your prediction.
